snippet.title: Hello Neighbor 2 Steam Demo?
snippet.description:
Missing Mr. Peterson?

We’ve arranged for you to spend some quality time with..err, avoiding him in our New Demo! Available on Steam on September 20th for a limited time, so keep an eye out!👀

Wishlist Hello Neighbor 2 & be the first to know when the new Demo drops!
https://tblink.co/HN2Steam

Join the Neighborhood: http://discord.gg/neighborgames

Be in the Know at www.helloneighbor2.com

Follow us on social media:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/NeighborGamesHQ

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/NeighborGamesHQ
